{"tid":1684718,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地豬乸人終於解決咗糧食問題,唔使只食草喇.","createTime":"2019-10-31T08:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T08:47:21.000Z","uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee80070ef5e5112b0e2e93a88a5ca2111bbdee5","tid":1684718,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:43:50.000Z","msg":"土饃, 諗起可以同POPO, 警嫂,小POPO一齊係大灣區一起食土,實在太幸福鳥. 仲有共同使用區塊鏈,徹底解決貧富同資源分配問題,唔使再用貨幣,唔怕老美制裁,甚至唔怕咩銀行唔比交易嘅問題.<br />\n感謝習總,感謝黨,感謝豬乸.<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1623912/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E6%BF%9F%E6%BA%90%E8%88%89%E8%BE%A6%E9%A3%9F%E5%9C%9F%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA-%E6%8E%83%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%80%E5%99%B8%E5%9C%9F%E9%A5%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1623912%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%25BA%2590%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%258E%2583%25E5%2585%2589-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2599%25B8%25E5%259C%259F%25E9%25A5%2583&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA%2FFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=b9410223\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1623912%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%25BA%2590%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%258E%2583%25E5%2585%2589-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2599%25B8%25E5%259C%259F%25E9%25A5%2583&h=09c3e858\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1623912/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E6%BF%9F%E6%BA%90%E8%88%89%E8%BE%A6%E9%A3%9F%E5%9C%9F%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA-%E6%8E%83%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%80%E5%99%B8%E5%9C%9F%E9%A5%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/_2019102910351736746.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F_2019102910351736746.jpg&h=16ee7e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/__2019102910351649828.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F__2019102910351649828.mp4&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA%2FFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=9ed47187\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F__2019102910351649828.mp4&h=8bc7acd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/__2019102910351649828.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n現代人常說的「下個月要吃土了！」原本是用於調侃錢花多了，需要節衣縮食，導致要食土。不過，在河南濟源有逾千名人真的食土，而且年年舉辦「吃土大會」，一噸的土也在一瞬間瘋搶光！<br />\n<br />\n第三屆吃土大會上周六（26日）在河南王屋山舉行，一聲令下，「選手」爭先恐後，仿如搶劫般，將台上的土饃盡掃進袋，更加有人跳上台中央撿，不消一會掃光一噸土饃。土饃屬於豫菜系聲稱含有豐富的鐵、鋅、鈣、鈉等元素，是河南濟源特色食品，加入了雞蛋、芝麻、蔥花等配料的麵團，必須用當地的觀音土炒熟，篩走多餘的土，即可食用，《本草綱目》亦有記載「壁土拌炒，借土氣助脾」。<br />\n<br />\n不過以往「觀音土」予人負面印象，在大饑荒時，不少災民將觀音土磨粉，摻和野菜、野草充飢，之後死亡。有醫生警告，過量進食會導致便秘、高血壓等問題，時移世易，遊子甚至說「一饃解鄉愁」。一位慕名而來的本地旅客說，在外地特別想吃家鄉的土饃特產，這是家鄉的代號，聽到王屋山有吃土大會，特別從外地返鄉，感受家鄉味。<br />\n<br />\n「吃土大會」的新聞，引來內地不少網民討論，由於鄰近「雙十一」，有網民調侃說，「雙十一之後，安排一下」；也有網民留言說：「我們山東也有，我小時候吃過！好香的！好吃！」。"},{"pid":"a08dd7dc23d41a4f813f22432ddf7153d429e10a","tid":1684718,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"正啊, 藍屍食土店, 黃色食土店.............<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x5S4jcrzCBE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx5S4jcrzCBE&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA%2FFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=fca63ad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x5S4jcrzCBE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y-HPgqdjY8I\" data